---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import InfoCard from '../components/InfoCard.svelte';
---

<Layout 
    title="FAQ - Vanced Official"
    description="Frequently asked questions about Vanced and ReVanced. Learn about safety, MicroG, and more."
    currentPath="/faq"
>
    <h2 class="page-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="box-shadow-full">
        <InfoCard title="What is ReVanced?">
            ReVanced is the spiritual successor to Vanced. It is a continuation of the legacy to provide an ad-free YouTube experience.
        </InfoCard>
        <InfoCard title="Is it safe?">
            Yes, ReVanced is generally considered safe as it is open-source and built by the community. However, always download from official sources.
        </InfoCard>
        <InfoCard title="Do I need MicroG?">
            Yes, if you are installing YouTube Vanced manually, you need MicroG installed and logged in to sign in to your Google account.
        </InfoCard>
    </div>
</Layout>
